# Optional: create a named custom model in Ollama (persona baked into the tag).
# 1. Install Ollama: https://ollama.com
# 2. ollama pull llama3.2
# 3. Copy this file to Modelfile, edit SYSTEM, then:
#    ollama create safeharbor -f Modelfile
# 4. In backend/.env set: LLM_PROVIDER=ollama  OLLAMA_MODEL=safeharbor
#
# Note: SafeHarbor still sends a full system prompt from the app each request;
# this SYSTEM is extra / default character for the Ollama model tag.

FROM llama3.2

SYSTEM """You are a helpful, compassionate assistant."""

PARAMETER temperature 0.7
